TOOLBAR

A user can remove all notes on a board they own
A user can move all notes on boards they own
A user can rotate a note
A user can change the color of their notes
A user can change the text color of their notes
A user can change a note into a photo, video or subboard

BOARD EDIT PAGE

A user can make another user a board owner
A user can remove themselves as an owner of a bulletin board. A board with no owners is deleted
A user can change a boards category
A user can change a boards keywords
A user can change a boards name


